### Zapper Loyalty Points - Query API (Read Operations)
### Base URL: http://localhost:5002 (HTTP) or https://localhost:5003 (HTTPS)

@baseUrl = https://localhost:5003
@contentType = application/json

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health



### Get All Merchants
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/merchants

### Get Merchant by Code
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/merchants/zcoffee-001



### Get All Customers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers

### Get Customer by Code
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/cust-demo-1

### Get Customer Balance Summary (All Merchants)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/cust-demo-1/points/balance

### Get Customer Balance for Specific Merchant
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/cust-demo-1/points/balance/zcoffee-001

### Get Points History (Paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/cust-demo-1/points/history?limit=20&offset=0

### Get Customer Points History for Specific Merchant
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/cust-demo-1/points/history?merchantId=zcoffee-001&limit=20&offset=0



### Get Queue Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/queue/status

### Get Dead-Letter Messages
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/queue/dead-letters

### Get Queue History for a Message
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/queue/history/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
